                <p>Entrants must be 15 years of age: £8.00 UKA Affiliated Runners £10.00 Non-Affiliated Runners, (Please add a further £2.00 for Race Day entry, subject to availability). UKA Multi-Terrain Race Licence 2018-35229</p>
