                <p>An exciting holiday club for children aged 5 - 11 will be held a All Saints' Church Hall, Onslow Gardens, Sanderstead from 28th - 30th August 2018, from 10 - 12.30 each day.</p>
                <p>The holiday club will be called 'Mission Rescue'; a secret agent theme that allows children each day to engage in missions, invent secret language, crack codes and deliver messages as we explore God's amazing rescue plan.</p>
